{
  "chapter": 2,
  "chapter_summary": "楚留香与李红袖在船头先后发现五具浮尸：第一具是朱砂门长老“杀手书生”西门千，喉部有窄剑贯穿伤；第二具是海南三剑之一的灵鹫子，头顶被一刀劈成两半，凶器疑似札木合的大风刀；第三具是札木合本人——这位“沙漠之王”竟死于天一神水之下，楚留香从皮靴、风霜面容等细节识破其身份。途中宋甜儿插嘴打趣，苏蓉蓉抱病登甲板。第五具神水宫女弟子被大风刀连肩削去一半，李红袖初断凶手为札木合，楚留香却指出札木合死后大风刀已落入第三人之手，凶手借刀杀人欲掩盖真相——此事远未结束，才刚刚开始。",
  "dialogues": [
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "想不到这人竟会是杀手书生西门千!",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 8,
      "line_end": 8
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "他杀死了左又铮，自己竟也死在别人手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 10,
      "line_end": 10
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但又是谁杀死他?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 12,
      "line_end": 12
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这是剑伤。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 16,
      "line_end": 16
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 18,
      "line_end": 18
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你说的若是无影神刀札木合，你就错了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 98,
      "line_end": 100
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "为什么会错?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 102,
      "line_end": 102
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "札木合号称中土刀法第一名家，刀法之快，无形无影，他一刀砍下时，灵鹫子也许还未瞧清是由何处来的。自然只有迎剑招架，而札木合使的一柄大风刀，乃海内十三件神兵利器之一，也足以砍断海南派剑。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 104,
      "line_end": 108
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "这岂非就是了么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 110,
      "line_end": 110
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "但你莫要忘了，札木合纵横戈壁大沙漠已有三十年，号称沙漠之王又怎会远来这里?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 112,
      "line_end": 112
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "你说不会，我却说会的。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 114,
      "line_end": 114
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你要和我赌一赌?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 116,
      "line_end": 116
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "我不和你赌，因为你输定了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 118,
      "line_end": 118
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你们赌吧，谁输了谁帮我洗半个月的碗。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 120,
      "line_end": 122
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_song_tian_er",
      "text": "小鬼，你在偷听。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 124,
      "line_end": 124
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "我虽然不敢看，听却敢听的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 126,
      "line_end": 126
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "喂!你瞧瞧这小鬼，打得好精明算盘，天下的便宜都被她一个人占尽了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 128,
      "line_end": 130
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你在等什么?等那札木合?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 134,
      "line_end": 134
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "也许……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 136,
      "line_end": 136
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你等不着的，这沙漠之王既不会来，纵然来了，也没有人能杀得死他。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 138,
      "line_end": 140
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "西门千与左又铮素少来往，为何杀了左又铮?灵鹫子与酉门千毫无冤仇，为何要杀死西门千?札木合与灵鹫子一个远在天边，一个远在海角，更是毫无关系，又为何要杀死灵鹫子?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 142,
      "line_end": 142
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "可见世上有许多事，是完全说不定的。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 144,
      "line_end": 144
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "好厉害的毒，我去叫蓉姐上来瞧瞧这究竟是什么毒。",
      "tone": "慌张",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 160,
      "line_end": 162
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "这毒蓉蓉也认不出的。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 164,
      "line_end": 164
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你又在吹了，你武功虽不错，但若论暗器，就未必比得上甜儿，若论易容术和下毒的本事，更万万比不上蓉姐。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 166,
      "line_end": 168
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "但这人中的并不完全是毒。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 170,
      "line_end": 170
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "不是毒药，难道是糖么?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 172,
      "line_end": 172
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "也可以算是糖……糖水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 174,
      "line_end": 174
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "糖水?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 176,
      "line_end": 176
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "这便是天池神水宫自水中提炼出的精英，江湖都称之为天一神水，而神水宫门人都称之为重水。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 178,
      "line_end": 180
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这真的就是比世上任何毒药都毒的天一神水?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 182,
      "line_end": 182
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "自然是真的，据说这天一神水一滴的分量，已比三百桶水都重，常人只要服下一滴，立刻全身爆裂而死!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 184,
      "line_end": 184
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "而且这天一神水五色无臭，试也试不出异状，所以，连这沙漠之王都难免中了暗算。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 186,
      "line_end": 188
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这……这人就是札木合?",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 190,
      "line_end": 190
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 192,
      "line_end": 192
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "他已变成这个样子，你怎么还能认得出他?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 194,
      "line_end": 194
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "他身穿的虽是寻常服色，但脚下却穿着双皮靴，显见他本是游牧之民，他身上皮肤虽细嫩，但面上却甚粗糙，显然是因为他来往沙漠，久经风尘之苦，他腰边虽有佩刀的钢环，但刀和刀鞘却全都不见了，显然是因为他使的乃是宝刀，所以才被人取去了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 196,
      "line_end": 198
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "有了这几点特征，自可说明他就是那沙漠之王，无影神刀札木合了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 200,
      "line_end": 202
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我看你可改行去做巡捕了，那你办起案子来，想必要比那天下第一名捕秃鹰还要厉害得多。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 204,
      "line_end": 206
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "还有，他身上挂着面银牌，上面刻的是只长着翅膀的飞骆驼，我若再瞧不出他是沙漠之王，就真是呆子了。",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 208,
      "line_end": 210
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你真是一个天才儿童。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 212,
      "line_end": 212
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这件事竟将沙漠之王与神水宫门下引动，可见关系必定不小，而此刻连沙漠之王都死了，可见……",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 214,
      "line_end": 214
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "你又想劝我罢手，是么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 216,
      "line_end": 216
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "我也不想劝你罢手，只望你能小心一些就是了。",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 218,
      "line_end": 218
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "闻得神水宫门下，俱都是人间的绝色，却不知比起咱们的三位姑娘来又如何?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 220,
      "line_end": 220
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你难道永远不能规矩些么?",
      "tone": "苦笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 222,
      "line_end": 222
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你只怕等不着了。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 226,
      "line_end": 226
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "若没有人死了，那么，这件事要着落在神水宫使者身上，这些人若是在争夺一件宝藏，那么，这宝藏便落在神水宫使者手上。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 228,
      "line_end": 230
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "若是有死人呢?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 232,
      "line_end": 232
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "无论还有多少人死，只要瞧最后一个人是死在谁手上，就有线索可寻。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 234,
      "line_end": 236
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这些高手们难道真会为了争夺宝藏而死?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 238,
      "line_end": 238
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "人为财死，这些人总也是人呀!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 240,
      "line_end": 240
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "能引动这许多绝代高手起了贪心的宝藏，想必一定惊人得很。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 242,
      "line_end": 244
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "你两个知唔知蓉姐有个表姑人佐神水宫?",
      "tone": "好奇",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 248,
      "line_end": 248
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "哦，蓉蓉竟有个表姑是神水宫门下么?这两天，她身子不知道是否已好些?不知道是否还在流鼻涕?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 250,
      "line_end": 250
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "你可是要她上来?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 252,
      "line_end": 252
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "算了，伤风的人，还是多躺躺的好。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 254,
      "line_end": 254
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "没关系，我的病反正已快好了，只要听见你说这句话，我……",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 256,
      "line_end": 256
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_song_tian_er",
      "speaker_name": "宋甜儿",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "蓉姐不要上他的当，他知道你来了，所以才故意说些关心你的话让你听。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 258,
      "line_end": 260
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_song_tian_er",
      "text": "就算是故意说的，只要他说出来，我就很开心了。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 262,
      "line_end": 264
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "蓉姐，风这么大，何必上来?小心又病倒在床上爬不起来，又害得我们这位多情的公子拿我们出气。",
      "tone": "担心",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 270,
      "line_end": 272
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "上面这么热闹，我还能在舱里呆得住么，何况，我也想瞧瞧，是不是真的会有神水宫使者到这里来。",
      "tone": "温柔",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 274,
      "line_end": 276
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "晚上冷，小心着凉。",
      "tone": "柔声",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 278,
      "line_end": 280
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "你总是只知关心别人，却不知道自己……你若有一分关心自己，又怎会病倒?",
      "tone": "无奈",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 282,
      "line_end": 282
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "是呀!像我们这些不生病的人，都是从来不关心他的。",
      "tone": "嘲讽",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 284,
      "line_end": 286
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "这么多心，人容易老的。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 288,
      "line_end": 288
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "我真是个又会多心，又会吃醋的小坏蛋，蓉姐为什么还要对我这么好?",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 290,
      "line_end": 290
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "text": "蓉姐，你看她是不是神水宫门下?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 306,
      "line_end": 306
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": null,
      "text": "这样的美人，是谁忍心向她下如此毒手?",
      "tone": "感叹",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 310,
      "line_end": 310
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "下这毒手的人，自己也死了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 312,
      "line_end": 312
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "你是说札木合?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 314,
      "line_end": 314
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "自然是札木合，除了他外，谁有这么快的刀?",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 316,
      "line_end": 316
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "嗯!",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 318,
      "line_end": 318
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "札木合发觉自己中毒，临死前拼尽余力，给了她一刀，他自然是满怀愤恨，所以这一刀才会这么毒，这么重。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 320,
      "line_end": 322
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "听起来到不是完全没有道理。",
      "tone": "调侃",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 324,
      "line_end": 324
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "现在，所有的线索都已断了，咱们也没事了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 326,
      "line_end": 328
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "没事了吗?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 330,
      "line_end": 330
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "人已全都死光了，还有什么事?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 332,
      "line_end": 332
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "你以为她真是死在札木合之手?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 334,
      "line_end": 334
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "难道不是?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 336,
      "line_end": 336
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "你莫忘了，札木合死后，他的大风刀已落在别人的手上，这人拿了大风刀杀死了她，正是要别人以为这件事已完全结束了。",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 338,
      "line_end": 340
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "呀!不错。",
      "tone": "惊讶",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 342,
      "line_end": 342
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "他既要别人认为此事结束，那么，此事就必定没有结束，在我说来，这件事正还未开始哩!",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 344,
      "line_end": 344
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "这件事，他是不愿别人插手的，是么?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 346,
      "line_end": 346
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "speaker_name": "李红袖",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "那么，他为何不将这些尸身完全毁去，别人若是根本瞧不清这些尸身，又怎能插得下手?",
      "tone": "疑问",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 348,
      "line_end": 348
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "speaker_name": "楚留香",
      "listener": "char_li_hong_xiu",
      "text": "这些人全都是江湖中的知名之士，而且甚至可说已有宗主的身份，他们若是突然一起失踪了，他们的门人子弟，不去追查明白么?",
      "tone": "微笑",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 350,
      "line_end": 350
    },
    {
      "speaker": "char_su_rong_rong",
      "speaker_name": "苏蓉蓉",
      "listener": "char_chu_liu_xiang",
      "text": "所以……",
      "tone": "陈述",
      "chapter": 2,
      "line_start": 352,
      "line_end": 352
    }
